Franklin Street, Fifth Floor, Boston, MA 02110-1301, USA.


**** Reviewed version ****

- Support at least vdr >= 2.4.4


# building (currently)

store reelbox utils directory outside VDR plugin tree

make:

LC_ALL=C make VANILLAVDR=1

Currently tested:
- Fedora 33 (using compat-ffmpeg28 and libpng12)
